<mjml>
  <mj-head>
    <mj-preview>
      Your PoeticMetric free trial ends tomorrow, don't miss out on valuable insights, upgrade to a paid plan or continue your journey with
      us.
    </mj-preview>

    <mj-attributes>
      <mj-button
          background-color="#3182CE"
          border-radius="6px"
          font-family="-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif"
          font-size="16px"
          font-weight="600"
      />

      <mj-text
          color="#2D3748"
          font-family="-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif"
          font-size="16px"
          font-weight="400"
          line-height="24px"
          padding-left="40px"
          padding-right="40px"
      />
    </mj-attributes>

    <mj-style inline="inline">
      a {
        font-weight: 700;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: #3182CE;
      }
    </mj-style>
  </mj-head>

  <mj-body background-color="#F7FAFC">
    <mj-section>
      <mj-column>
        <mj-spacer height="20px" />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <mj-section background-color="#EBF8FF" border-radius="8px 8px 0 0">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-image
            width="200px"
            src="https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/698079/139349672-47706255-455f-4859-955c-2d1e927add90.png"
            align="center"
            alt="PoeticMetric Logo"
            href="{{.FrontendBaseUrl}}"
        />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <mj-section background-color="#ffffff" border-radius="0 0 6px 6px">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text>
          <p>Greetings,</p>

          <p>
            <strong>This is just a friendly reminder that your 30-day free trial of PoeticMetric ends tomorrow.</strong>
            We wanted to take this opportunity to thank you for trying out our analytics platform, and we hope that you've been able to gain
            valuable insights into your website's traffic during your trial period.
          </p>

          <p>
            As your trial comes to an end, we want to remind you that you can continue using PoeticMetric by upgrading to one of our paid
            plans. Our plans are designed to fit the needs of any organization and budget.
          </p>

          <p>
            You can find more information on our <a href="{{.FrontendBaseUrl}}/pricing">pricing</a> page.
          </p>

          <p>
            If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to reach out to our support team. We're always here to help.
          </p>
        </mj-text>

        <mj-text>
          <p>Cheers,</p>

          <p>The PoeticMetric Team</p>
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <mj-section padding-top="8px">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text font-size="12px" align="center">Copyright Â© WebGazer, Inc.</mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
  </mj-body>
</mjml>
